無一被起訴<br />\n<br />\n事件過後，一班政棍竟妄想把元朗無差別打人事件與示威者混為一談，將示威者與暴力掛勾，混淆視聽，當人民選擇沉默的同時，面對的卻是當權者步步進逼，除了走上街頭，手無寸鐵的市民還能用什麼方式表達不滿？<br />\n<br />\n當你天真的以為他們會悔過時，別忘了還有8.11&mdash;更黑暗的一天<br />\n<br />\n當管治者不斷破壞我們的核心價值，新聞自由、集會自由、言論自由不斷被扼殺，我們的法制、人權受到破壞，誠信、廉潔蕩然無存的情況下，當面對欺壓，我們選擇視若無睹，當我們選擇繼續沉默，香港的核心價值將在無聲中死去。你願意站岀來為自己、為下一代爭取更好的香港嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你班連登傻仔，入乜撚嘢機場？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0d8bdf689a0c79e482513ef4c8cfc9d7ed4bd697","tid":1450223,"uid":33907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:19:11.000Z","msg":"找一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵人屌到佢爆曬啲料出嚟"},{"pid":"f16642f4440f19ac7bf84a0ac076674b1ddbd278","tid":1450223,"uid":10056,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9e706c20f8ac9d80586741f5114ebb10340c9fbf","tid":1450223,"uid":281444,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:17:54.000Z","msg":"找一找一，是暗號嗎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:19:26.000Z","msg":"屌你個肥仔真係唔識架喎  1仔呀 擰轉面抬高個屎忽啦"},{"pid":"516797e2aa062b2bc87f102ee77effb2902afc38","tid":1450223,"uid":61882,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4c24928ecac9d24aa08806471012c9f115a3e236","tid":1450223,"uid":66824,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:17:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好討論樓主係咪gay<br />\n<br />\n快d好似釣狗公咁<br />\nChok佢